  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/455770/extras/89ae16db2e4293e30eb3629730415568.avif?t=1499900439\" width=630 height=97 /></span><br>YamaYama is a whacky party game where you complete all sorts of mini-games to collect points on your path to victory. Most of the game modes utilise the FatSuit mechanic, where characters blow out and push other players away. It is made with easy-to-learn controls, so you can play with both video game veterans and newbies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/455770/extras/dd2ede06e4ef7c66e48d03d86c88b26f.avif?t=1499900439\" width=630 height=97 /></span><br>•\t2-4 player local and online multiplayer<br>•\tSingle player with 1-3 Monkey AI bots<br>•\tAn excellent new game for the party!<br>•\t23 game modes<br>•\t6 characters<br>•\tThe ultimate new game for the party!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/455770/extras/2d27dd34dca5e84555a9434faf231baf.avif?t=1499900439\" width=630 height=105 /></span><br>•\t\t<br>•\t<br>•\t<br>•\tJoin the Discussions if you have any questions!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/455770/extras/89ae16db2e4293e30eb3629730415568.avif?t=1499900439\" width=630 height=97 /></span><br>YamaYama is a whacky party game where you complete all sorts of mini-games to collect points on your path to victory. Most of the game modes utilise the FatSuit mechanic, where characters blow out and push other players away. It is made with easy-to-learn controls, so you can play with both video game veterans and newbies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/455770/extras/dd2ede06e4ef7c66e48d03d86c88b26f.avif?t=1499900439\" width=630 height=97 /></span><br>•\t2-4 player local and online multiplayer<br>•\tSingle player with 1-3 Monkey AI bots<br>•\tAn excellent new game for the party!<br>•\t23 game modes<br>•\t6 characters<br>•\tThe ultimate new game for the party!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/455770/extras/2d27dd34dca5e84555a9434faf231baf.avif?t=1499900439\" width=630 height=105 /></span><br>•\t\t<br>•\t<br>•\t<br>•\tJoin the Discussions if you have any questions!",
